# 57. Hugsanlegt provider interface

```ts
type ForecastRequest = {
  routePoints: {
    id: string;
    latitude: number;
    longitude: number;
    elevationM?: number;
  }[];

  timeFrom: string;
  timeTo: string;
};

interface ForecastProvider {
  id: ForecastSourceId;
  displayName: string;

  getForecast(
    request: ForecastRequest
  ): Promise<NormalizedForecastPoint[]>;

  getCapabilities(): {
    supportsCoordinates: boolean;
    supportsStations: boolean;
    supportedMetrics: string[];
    typicalTimeStepMinutes?: number;
  };
}
```

Þá getur samanburðarvélin vitað hvaða breytur er raunhæft að bera saman.

